'''Paul Blake''' is an [[Wikipedia:English people|English]] actor who portrayed the [[bounty hunter]] [[Greedo]] in [[Star Wars: Episode IV A New Hope|''Star Wars'': Episode IV ''A New Hope'']].<ref name="Databank">{{DB|character|greedo|Greedo}}</ref> A production photograph related to the scene with [[Jabba Desilijic Tiure|Jabba]] the [[Hutt]] in [[Docking Bay 94]] shows Blake putting on a [[Rodian]] costume on the set.<ref name="Actor">{{WebCite|url=https://www.elitesignatures.co.uk/product/paul-blake-signed-greedo-10x8|text=Paul Blake Signed Greedo 10×8|work=[https://www.elitesignatures.co.uk elitesignatures.co.uk]|archivedate=20240213072022}}</ref>

He is credited by [[John Mollo]] as portraying a 'plutonian' in [[Star Wars: Episode IV A New Hope|''Star Wars'': Episode IV ''A New Hope'']] as documented in the [[1979]] book [[The Art of Star Wars Episode IV: A New Hope|''The Art of Star Wars'']].<ref name="TAoSW">[[The Art of Star Wars Episode IV: A New Hope|''The Art of Star Wars'']]</ref>

